headline: Add Action to add cc'ed people as reviewers
body: This provides a mechanism for non-triager/reviewer/committer PR authors to request reviews through GitHub. Anyone that is referenced by `cc @username` in a PR body will be added as a reviewer (GitHub will limit the reviewers to those with actual permissions to leave reviews so the script to add can be simple).

headline: [microNPU] Removing constant args from PrimFunc
body:
Before this commit, microNPU creates PrimFunc as if
it accepts constants from the callee. This commit
changes the PrimFunc to remove the constants as an
argument to PrimFunc as they are not provided from
the main function.

headline: Add action to label mergeable PRs
body: Developers often have to ping a committer once their PRs are both passing in CI and are approved. This helps facilitate this process by marking such PRs with a label `ready-for-merge` so committers can easily filter for outstanding PRs that need attention.

headline: [microNPU] Refactor base address determination to codegen
body:
This commit introduces BaseAddress ObjectRef to determine
base addresses in the codegen for microNPU. This is
required when multiple memory pools become available. Thus,
base addresses could not be statically determined in the
source module.

Change-Id: I6cfa578af0318bbe07d3bb9415df7bdd839611d3
author: manupa-arm
